2004-10-12 06:27:02  dangelo  (dangelo)

	* configure: removed configure, it is created from configure.ac

	* BUGS, COPYING, Makefile, Makefile.am, configure, configure.ac:
	switched to automake/autoconf.	Thanks to Douglas Wilkins for
	the patch!

2004-10-11 21:12:21  dangelo  (dangelo)

	* src/Panorama/Stitcher.cpp, src/include/PT/PanoramaMemento.h,
	src/include/PT/RemappedPanoImage.h, src/include/PT/Stitcher.h,
	src/include/vigra_ext/ROIImage.h, src/include/vigra_ext/blend.h,
	src/tests/vigra_ext.cpp: fixed crashes while remapping and
	blending. nona should be useable again

	* src/tools/zhang_undistort.cpp: patch to compile zhang_undistort
	utility, can be used to undistort images using the zhang
	distortion model. The calibration tool can be found at
	http://loper.org/~matt/CamChecker/CamChecker_docs/html/index.html

