2004-09-08 23:33:33  dangelo  (dangelo)

	* src/tools/zhang_undistort.cpp: simple test tool to
	undistort images according to the zhang camera model.
	an opensource calibration tool is available from
	http://www.loper.org/~matt/CamChecker/CamChecker_docs/html/index.html

	* src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp,
	src/hugin/huginApp.cpp, src/include/PT/ImageGraph.h,
	src/nona_gui/nona_gui.cpp: Fixes for Mac OSX compilation. Thanks
	to Ippei UKAI for the activity on the Mac

	* src/hugin/huginApp.cpp: minor change

	* src/Makefile: do not build PanoImage by default

	* src/hugin/Makefile, src/hugin/NonaStitcherPanel.cpp,
	src/include/PT/Stitcher.h, src/tests/Makefile, src/tools/Makefile:
	minor changes (DEBUG output etc.)

	* src/hugin/CPFineTuneFrame.cpp, src/hugin/CPZoomDisplayPanel.cpp,
	src/include/hugin/CPFineTuneFrame.h,
	src/include/hugin/CPZoomDisplayPanel.h: added window to display
	the magnified and perspetive corrected control points.	DISABLED,
	because of a bug in the orientation estimation.

	* src/tests/vigra_ext.cpp: added some test that compare the two
	correlation routines

	* src/makefiles/rules.mk: abort building after a compiler error
	has occured.

	* src/hugin/RunOptimizerFrame.cpp, src/hugin/RunStitcherFrame.cpp:
	better output parsing of PTStitcher and PTOptimizer (optimizing
	progress works properly with newer Pano Tools library)

	* src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp: removed stupid cut'n'paste error that
	created the nona output files before the stitching.  This broke
	nona stitching if the correct file extension was specified.

	* src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp,
	src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp, src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h,
	src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h, src/include/panoinc_WX.h,
	src/include/vigra_ext/Correlation.h: added new correlation
	function that will also search for rotated patches.  it must
	be enabled in the config file (or registry), by setting
	CPEditorPanel/RotationSearch = 1 the angle interval that should
	be tried can be specified with

	CPEditorPanel/RotationStartAngle CPEditorPanel/RotationStopAngle
	CPEditorPanel/RotationSteps

	* src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp: fixed control point parsing bug
	with newer pano12.dll's

	* src/common/utils.cpp: fixed error when the path to an output
	file contained a .

2004-08-30 22:58:32  dangelo  (dangelo)

	* src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp: fix endless loop on removing images,
	looks like an unsigned int can get negative with the gcc 3.3
	under linux, that is (! (uint >= 0)) can become true..

	* src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp: fixed a typo (file dialog was called
	save instead of load)

