2004-07-06 21:53:38  dangelo  (dangelo)

	* src/include/hugin/ImageCache.h,
	src/include/hugin/PreviewPanel.h, src/hugin/ImageCache.cpp,
	src/hugin/PreviewPanel.cpp, src/include/PT/ImageTransforms.h,
