	physical focal length should be entered.

	* src/hugin/PanoDruid.cpp: - removed lens nr druid hint. its a
	program error to have images without lens - changed control point
	hint to consider 1 image panos as a special case - added hint
	to run the optimizer (detected if all images are still at 0,0,0)

	* src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp: - fixed a crash if the estimated
	position was outside of the image

	* src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp, src/Panorama/PanoramaMemento.cpp,
	src/include/PT/PanoCommand.h, src/include/PT/PanoramaMemento.h:
	changed focal length handling.	- crop factor is calculated
	based on sensor diagonals..
	  its a bit strange that my camera EXIF data reports non square
	  pixels...

	- changes to lens variables are applied to all images.

